Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:04.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:09.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So we're in the same class \Nthis year, too? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:10.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:13.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're happy about it, Ri-chan, I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:24.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! Well don't you look chipper!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that happy about being in \Nclass 10 with all the rowdy kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:41.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't used to being split into \Na different class from his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sentaro's first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.72,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You've got a petal in your hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'll get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.28,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.02,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.49,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's cruel... We just did \Nself-introductions in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You set up his ticket for the \Nsleeper, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.18,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.20,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,He said to keep it a secret from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I had a nice trip. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:08.16,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:11.54,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We should've decided the class rep \Nby drawing lots in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.84,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,No kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.71,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard there's already \Na fight in class 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.94,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad I wasn't put in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you done already, Boxing Club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had a little \Nmore spirit than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:33.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:37.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "Hi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting on the first \Nday of the new school year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just gettin' a little exercise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:47.14,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun. Been too \Nlong since I had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going over there \Nwith that banged-up face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:18.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you take this guy \Nto the infirmary and patch him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, he's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It still hurts a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but I should get used to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:39.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The pain will go away and I should \Nbe able to relax and smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.71,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to submit this painting \Nto this year's public exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.22,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one Sentaro-kun modeled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:57.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's okay. You don't have \Nto force yourself to give me feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. I don't know much about art...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.82,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's a strange thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,After all, painting and jazz are \Nrelatively close cousins, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.72,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,A painting is created on \Na space called the canvas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.78,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,while jazz is created during \Na time called the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:20.41,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's like etching your living \Nself into that place and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.22,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that. I \Nwas only repeating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:28.51,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san was talking about that \Nwhen I went down to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.02,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.43,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,It's very interesting to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:37.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk to him more \Nabout all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:43.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I went to Tokyo during spring break...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:48.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And I dropped by Brother Jun's boarding \Nhouse, but he wasn't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.03,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he hadn't been \Nback for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so there were a lot of letters \Nstuffed in his mail slot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said he might be staying \Nover at another person's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.02,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,One of those letters may \Nhave been important...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.14,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Just put a little spit on cuts like \Nthese and they'll heal up fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do if it gets infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko... I'm glad you're in \Nthe same class as Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:37.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, would you look \Nafter him more instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I'd better get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:48.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Glad I caught up to \Nyou before you went home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are those tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This glob looks like a tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.06,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,That's the tear of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,In Greek mythology, the god Apollo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:05.52,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,fell in love with Daphne, \Nthe daughter of a river god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.49,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He became obsessed and chased her all \Naround, but she wouldn't stop running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.57,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,At last, she gave Apollo \Nthe ultimate rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,by turning into a bay laurel tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.83,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What an awful case of heartbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.08,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he would cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:23.21,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He's so grief-stricken that he fashions \Na wreath out of the laurel tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.33,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is Matsuoka Seiji-kun, \Na second-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.87,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Great Hope of East High's Art Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.74,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it! You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.98,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi Sentaro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.48,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,We're both in class 10, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.49,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie... Do you remember \Nthat guy from last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' the chills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.39,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, Sentaro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free on our next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.66,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get you a present \Nas thanks for being my model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Apollo, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I could never see this guy \Nwearing a laurel wreath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, do you have detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I forgot my math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual for someone as \Nlevel-headed as you, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was level-headed? \NI'm careless as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I get more absent-minded in the \Nspring, but better snap out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's from "The Sound of Music".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.05,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I figured you would \Nlike that movie, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:56.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to, but before I knew \Nit, it'd already stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:59.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was a good movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How could I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:05.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I thought I'd be \Nable to see it anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"My Favorite Things".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, better not... I had my shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:51.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there was somethin' I \Nwanted your advice about, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,About... my date...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,With Yurika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll give the perfect advice \Nto a romantic beginner like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?! What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:14.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,On a one-on-one date, you're sure to \Nfreeze up and blow the whole deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle a date, piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure! You really think \Nyou can keep TPO in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:26.02,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,TPO: Time Place Occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,in front of that princess \Nand behave accordingly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,T... TP...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it is? You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But for your own sake, you better not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,TP...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everyone would just \Nstop falling in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:53.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That dope! Well, don't \Nblame me for what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:08.73,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro-kun, don't hold back. Tell \Nme if you see something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:13.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nah. I never get \Nexpensive stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:17.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Even this jacket is a hand-me-down \Nfrom Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.46,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:25.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And from then on, all we talked \Nabout was Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:31.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When Brother Jun was in high \Nschool, nobody was cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He was good at fightin', smart too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.71,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We had a good time talkin' about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:42.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...but now all I got left is a feelin' \Nof emptiness in the pit of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did your date go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Course it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:53.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A date is a \Npiece of cake for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't go well at all, did \Nit? Just like I predicted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... Stay away from her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:09.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are dense, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:18.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Any way you look at it, you and a refined \Ngirl like that just don't match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you call being \N"out of your depth"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. I went too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kawabuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.92,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you went on a date with Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.53,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,She said she had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, is that true?! Did \Nshe say anythin' else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.67,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.61,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! She said you were \Nhandsome, Kawabuchi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.73,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,and that maybe she'll \Nhold your hand next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Richie, you're here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:09.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wanna try playin' "My \NFavorite Things" again together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:15.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? I thought he'd be mad \Nat me for what I said at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but he seems to be in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought only jazz was allowed in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:31.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that kid with the mushroom \Ncut, Matsuoka, forced it on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't refuse, so I just carried it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, making a nice \Nfriend that lends you records...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.86,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.85,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come upstairs a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What, did a new record come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.52,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just come up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is he... going to listen to that record?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:03.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What am I so anxious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.31,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.28,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you listen to the record \NI gave you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:15.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I can't get into music that \Nhas girls squealin' over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.87,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the purpose of making music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.97,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna become popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't really care about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.55,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanna be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.86,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to become a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.56,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:39.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Are those the underpants \Nof somebody who aims to be a star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.56,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.93,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot of brothers, so if \NI don't stake my claim like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.67,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,they'll disappear in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:49.34,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,And we're poor, so we can't \Nafford to buy new ones often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:53.18,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Amongst all my brothers, I'm \Ncalled the "good-for-nothing".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.37,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Really, singing is the \Nonly thing I'm good at...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:15:01.13,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna prove that I can become somebody \Nwho's able to support his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:07.43,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,To me, this band is the first step. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.54,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi-kun, I need your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.34,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.42,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, Maruo-kun! \NMuch better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.54,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:40.48,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, now all we need is a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:44.00,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, are you gonna tell me \Nwho it is you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.06,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll find out soon enough. \NBe ready for a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,No school tomorrow, so if you're \Nfree, wanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma told me to take the munchkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:03.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But lookin' after them alone is a tough job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd ask you along to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:10.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there. You free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we have us a \Nclammin' contest at the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? "Clammin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I like clamming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's "clammin"? Is it \Nsome kind of competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru-san! Clamming means \Ndigging up clams at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's confusing when this guy \Ncalls it a contest or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going too, Ri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.46,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then the threesome's set! \NThis is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to mentally \Nprepare myself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:53.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If those two have a romantic moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:58.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll casually get out of their way \Nand just pray for Ri-chan's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Or that was the idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but maybe that's a non-issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.62,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I got a hamaguri clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:10.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's a short-necked clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.85,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Fancy meeting you here, Kawabuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.48,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.12,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What cute little girls and boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.14,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's a place over there \Nwhere you can find a lot of razor clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.27,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Razors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.95,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Ritsuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.73,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you from Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,She said you were exceptionally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.99,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are the razor clams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.90,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're right over here. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:40.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy? \NSweet-talking everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't criticize the guy \Nwhen you don't know 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.75,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.93,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting, right?! Who wants to try it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.59,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.31,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.45,Main Dialog,Taiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:03.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having a good \Ntime over there. Shall we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:08.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. For some reason, that Matsuoka \Ncharacter rubs me the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.47,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taiichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.99,Main Dialog,Taiichi,0000,0000,0000,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.00,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You were surprised when the \Ncrab pinched you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness that's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:33.09,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiji! Don't tell me\Nyour drummer is Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.46,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anybody but him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.12,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm against it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:41.64,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't as scary as you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:46.27,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is set him \Nfree from what's tying him down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.29,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,and then everything should \Nwork out the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Catchin' any short-necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Better not underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at this kind of simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.54,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I ain't gonna lose neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Clammin' contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What do I get if I win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How about the record that \NRi-chan's dad gave you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it! 'Cause I'm gonna win anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.96,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Beatles record?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.08,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kawabuchi-kun, did you listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard it. Wasn't bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.06,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Did it stir up your interest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go that far. But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinkin' I'll help you out with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,that band you're gonna have \Nfor the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.27,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You'll join my rock band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.01,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:39.95,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.94,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:46.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna be away 'til \Nthe festival's over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.08,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We're just gonna be apart for a while, Nishimi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.21,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's send each other letters, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,In a pig's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong about you, traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:06.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me! I don't \Nwant to listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:30.37,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I acted like an angry little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:36.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But being separated from him \Nscares the hell out of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:39.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I abandoned him without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming here, I'd forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm not good at getting \Nalong with other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's better this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've made it \Nthis far all on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No problem... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.01,Main Dialog,Bartender,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu-chan, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.62,Main Dialog,Bartender,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the end of the counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.75,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
